{"tid":2146773,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Miss Pun突然話要結婚喎","createTime":"2020-08-08T20:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T02:56:58.000Z","uid":306528,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fd29fb652f5f931dee88171cb4e2714fdf8da139","tid":2146773,"uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:02:51.000Z","msg":"我要結婚了。<br />\n<br />\n沒有懷孕，只是緣分到了。感謝對方三年來伴我走過人生的高峰與低谷、疾病與健康。<br />\n<br />\n不會復出，IG和FB App都del了兩個星期，因為要公佈這個消息才安裝一下，不是故意不回覆大家的訊息，而是真正的我不喜歡社交。<br />\n<br />\n也不會舉行婚禮，因為疫情，疫情過後其實也不會補辦，因為我不喜歡。<br />\n<br />\n純粹循例通知一下認識的人，不是邀請大家或要求給禮金，祝各位生活愉快。"},{"pid":"41f96bfb7a91891964116617989814abe50b1bb0","tid":2146773,"uid":251001,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:04:09.000Z","msg":"係咪同唐仔結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a942a08594042038aaf8705834ae855ceedbebf","tid":2146773,"uid":242184,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:05:40.000Z","msg":"都要入去坐啦 仲結乜"},{"pid":"6ebe8c7f110328632ee8abe3d385bcb24a28ba0a","tid":2146773,"uid":210100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:06:35.000Z","msg":"不喜歡社交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係因為比人拉咗先del?"},{"pid":"f3359ac77c1b811a2a7ebf6447081cc84243cf19","tid":2146773,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41f96bfb7a91891964116617989814abe50b1bb0","tid":2146773,"uid":251001,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:04:09.000Z","msg":"係咪同唐仔結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:07:09.000Z","msg":"同個唐氏仔結"},{"pid":"ee8ff3ea9c37ed9126a487ffebfb8c89fe0641bd","tid":2146773,"uid":339751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:08:17.000Z","msg":"呢啲過氣電